aHei&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;amp;quot;, sans-serif;\&lt;span class="hljs-string"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;gt;被开除军籍的冷锋&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span style&amp;#61;\&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; font-family: &amp;amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;amp;quot;, sans-serif;\&lt;span class="hljs-string"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;em&amp;gt;&amp;#xff08;吴京饰演&amp;#xff09;&amp;lt;/em&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span style&amp;#61;\&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; font-family: &amp;amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;amp;quot;, sans-serif;\&lt;span class="hljs-string"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;gt;本是因找杀害龙小云的凶手&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span style&amp;#61;\&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; font-family: &amp;amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;amp;quot;, sans-serif;\&lt;span class="hljs-string"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;em&amp;gt;&amp;#xff08;余男饰演&amp;#xff09;&amp;lt;/em&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span style&amp;#61;\&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; font-family: &amp;amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;amp;quot;, sans-serif;\&lt;span class="hljs-string"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;gt;来到非洲&amp;#xff0c;但是却突然被卷入一场非洲国家的叛乱。因为国家之间政治立场的关系&amp;#xff0c;中国军队无法在非洲实行武装行动撤离华侨。而作为退伍老兵的&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;a href&amp;#61;\&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%86%B7%E9%94%8B/17576501\&lt;span class="hljs-string"&gt;&amp;#34; target&amp;#61;\&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;_blank\&lt;span class="hljs-string"&gt;&amp;#34; style&amp;#61;\&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;text-indent: 28px; text-align: start;\&lt;span class="hljs-string"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;gt;冷锋&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span style&amp;#61;\&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; font-family: &amp;amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;amp;quot;, sans-serif;\&lt;span class="hljs-string"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;gt;无法忘记曾经为军人的使命&amp;#xff0c;本来可以安全撤离的他毅然决然地回到了沦陷区&amp;#xff0c;孤身一人带领身陷屠杀中的同胞和难民&amp;#xff0c;展开生死逃亡。随着斗争的持续&amp;#xff0c;体内的狼性逐渐复苏&amp;#xff0c;最终闯入战乱区域&amp;#xff0c;为同胞而战斗&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span style&amp;#61;\&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12px; font-family: &amp;amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;amp;quot;, sans-serif;\&lt;span class="hljs-string"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;sup&amp;gt;&amp;amp;nbsp;&amp;lt;/sup&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span style&amp;#61;\&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; font-family: &amp;amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;amp;quot;, sans-serif;\&lt;span class="hljs-string"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;gt;&amp;amp;nbsp;。&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#96;.match(/&amp;lt;img src&amp;#61;\&lt;span class="hljs-string"&gt;&amp;#34;([\S\s]*?)&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;/)[1]
